This is a '''timeline of [[Sudan]]ese history''', comprising important legal and territorial changes and political events in Sudan and its predecessor states. To read about the background to these events, see [[History of Sudan]]. See that the [[list of governors of pre-independence Sudan]] and [[list of heads of state of Sudan]].
